<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_164" id="82r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_164_r1l26"><expan>Pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu ſand Sebolt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_164_r1l27">Erſamer vnd lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . wır <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l28">Daʒ Jr vns bey <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet ſouıl eẅch füklıch ſey . vvıe ſıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l29"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıgſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> kunıgs vnd auch des <expan>Co<ex>n</ex>cılıu<ex>m</ex>s</expan> lewft vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l30">ſache nu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd gemacht <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd auch ob Jr ıht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> lewft oder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l31">mer weſt dıe vns ʒu <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> gebüren . vnd vns darinn eẅr <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l32">vnd guten <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweıſet . Als etc das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_164" id="82r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> zu sand Sebolt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz
                        ir uns bey <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, sovil ewch füklich sey, wie
                        sich <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> des <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        kunigs, und auch des <expan>co<ex>n</ex>ciliu<ex>m</ex>s</expan> lewft und
                        sache nu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> und gemacht
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch ob ir iht
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> lewft oder mer west, die uns zu
                                <expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> gebüren, und uns darinn ewr
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und guten
                            <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweiset, als etc. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
